data.description: Price reduced! Welcome to this adorable well kept 2 bedroom, 1 bath home with a nice open front porch, newer  front steps and  sidewalk. Many updates have been done. Newer roof, windows, wood floors, new shower, newer electrical, boiler and air conditioning & glass block in basement. Fully fenced yard with a freshly painted 1 car garage. Ceiling fans. Appliances included, Stove Refrigerator, Washer and Dryer. Don't wait..at this price it will sell fast!
